%% Request lifecycle — edge to data and back
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as browser
    participant FE as Next.js + BFF (/api/[...path])
    participant SVC as FastAPI service
    participant MW as middleware chain
    participant H as route handler
    participant DB as Postgres (via PgBouncer)

    U->>FE: fetch /api/articles
    Note over FE: read JWT from httpOnly cookie
    FE->>SVC: GET /articles (Authorization: Bearer, X-Correlation-ID)
    SVC->>MW: CorrelationIdMiddleware (assign/propagate id)
    MW->>MW: JWTAuthMiddleware (verify RS256 locally — or bypass if DISABLE_AUTH)
    MW->>H: dispatch
    H->>DB: SELECT … (AsyncSession via Depends)
    DB-->>H: rows
    H-->>MW: response model
    MW-->>SVC: + correlation header
    SVC-->>FE: JSON
    FE-->>U: rendered data
